com.tsgrp.migration.queuepop

Class QueuePopulatorXml

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener
      • com.tsgrp.migration.queuepop.QueuePopulatorXml
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PipelinePopulateQueueEventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    QueuePopulatorXmlWithAssociations

    public class QueuePopulatorXml
extends AbstractListener
implements PipelinePopulateQueueEventListener
    An XML file queue populator that works based on XPath queries. Arguments include the path to a file or folder. If a file is provided, the queue populator will process the single file. If a folder path is provided, the queue populator will process all XML files with in the folder or any of its subfolders.
